The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | CAB to host national U-16 meet
                                                   CAB to host national U-16 meet
            OUR CORRESPONDENT                      
	Guwahati: The Orissa Cricket Association will host the East Zone National One-dayers this year. The association will also host the under-19 one-day tournament for the Vinoo Mankad Trophy.         
	The Cricket Association of Bengal will host the Vijay Merchant Trophy (Under-16) and the Polly Umrigar Trophy inter-school tournaments later this year.         
	The Assam Cricket Association will host the East Zone womens Twenty20 and inter-state one-day tournaments.         
	The allotment of venues was finalised at a meeting of the BCCI East Zone committee on Wednesday. The under-19 girls zonal tournament will be held in Tripura while the Jharkhand Cricket Association will host the mens zonal Twenty20.         
	It was also decided to hold the batting and bowling coaching camps for the junior and senior players under specialised coaches in Orissa and Bengal tentatively in February.                                                                                                                       
